      <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:3;48:10" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/schemeref.dita">See <xref class="- topic/xref " href="subjectScheme.dita" xtrc="xref:6;48:47" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/schemeref.dita" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?>subjectScheme<?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">The <xmlelement class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlelement " xtrc="xmlelement:2;7:28" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/subjectScheme.dita">subjectScheme</xmlelement> element is a specialization of       <xmlelement class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlelement " xtrc="xmlelement:3;8:19" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/subjectScheme.dita">map</xmlelement>; it defines taxonomic subjects and controlled values.</desc></xref>.</p>
